CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS AND ADMINISTRATIVE ACTIONS

September 10, 2003

MERIT DECISIONS WITHOUT OPINIONS

Board of Tax Appeals, Nos. 2003-T-211, 2003-T-213, 2003-T-215 and 2003-T-217. On motion to remand to the Ohio Board of Tax Appeals. Motion granted.
